    "The authors then rescale image intensity and remove noise using filters and morphological techniques.",
    "Candidate signal objects were identified based on adaptive edge/line detection and morphological attributes such as length and area.",
    "Additionally, high-intensity pixels near these objects were considered.",
    "In a postsegmentation step, objects considered artifacts were removed.",
    "It is important to note that passing fibers and terminals were not differentiated."
